title: 043: What we think about Planet Fitness
description: Here's a quiz. Planet Fitness is... 1) An inexpensive gym for the masses. 2) A place where fitness minded people can work out without fear of judgment. Only one of the above statements is true. Sal, Adam and Justin have some pretty strong feelings about Planet Fitness and their policies. Tune in to hear what the REALLY think...
